social_posts.post_text: Had to see what the AI had in store for me.

Back to fighting on the big screen! Had a great time acting in the new movie “As Good As Dead” produced by my buddies @mclebanoff owner of @odysseymotionpicturesofficial @justindnesbitt and written by @officialmichaeljai distributed by @goldwynfilms  on multiple platforms including Hulu, iTunes, Amazon, Google Play, Vudu, Microsoft, Redbox, and major cable providers. Also had a great time sharing the screen with @louismandylorofficial who is the brother of @realcostasmandylor who was a lead in the movie I just directed!  Hope you enjoy this film!! Show them how ranger fans support a ranger!

Man oh man!! We had the best time with Malachi’s first santa experience.
It took a second to warm up to santa but so glad we got these memorable moments!
All of Malachi’s grandparents joined the party too!!😁

Sorry last post… Me and Victoria can not wait to have more babies! Malachi has been such a blessing to our lives and he has open our eyes to so many new perspectives. And of course our amazing santa Garry who was an actor in a movie I directed came out and was the best santa in the world!

He might be mama’s boy but he’s dada’s little man! Swipe left to see my dad and I in the same pose. Like father like son.  Thank you dad for loving me to the fullest.  I get to look down at my son the way you looked at me. #dadlife
ke huy quan I’m excited for your Oscar win! It was great sitting and talking with you and you are the real deal! Dreams do come true!

If you are looking to film a movie or need a place to build sets send me a DM! We’re in atlanta georgia now and we’re ready to rock! We’ve already had 3 films use our studios! I also have camera lighting gear packages for rent as well as a full grip truck! Let’s go!!!!!

Amazed that this is the very land where wakanda stood! As a director & actor I’m always so excited about the process of film making! The vision of the director and production designers to bring sets to life is a process that doesn’t get the attention it deserves but wow wow wow! So glad for the move we made already connected with the largest studios in nation and the people here are outstanding! 💪🏽😁 #trilithstudios #trilith #trilithproductions #marvel #avengers

I’m so proud to be a daddy! I’ve been blessed to spend so much time at home with my wife and Malachi.  This past year has been life changing in so many ways but through it all!! The good and and bad… having your family by your side is the best gift in the world! Thank you for the doors that are opening and thank you for closing certain doors. God we trust you! 
‭‭Nahum‬ ‭1‬:‭7‬ ‭
I missed my calling at the circus! @brennanmejia thanks for giving me a taste of the business! 🙏🏽😁

Wow, I can’t believe time flies so fast!!! I enjoy being married to the most incredible woman in the world!  I also love being a father to my life changing son! I can’t believe Malachi will be 2 and two weeks!  He’s changed me… he’s changed both of us!  Through all the years of being single, I never knew that Life would actually start once you found your wife and started your family.  As I mentor different people who are still struggling to find their soulmate, I encourage them to wait and God will bless you with the right person, and you will know if they are the one.  I love to serve my wife and I love to serve and Mentor my son. To all my friends and fans… I’m praying that you have a successful week, month, and year! God bless!! 🙏🏽😁
We showed Malachi how to find peaceful streams…🙏🏽😁 we had to make sure he didn’t slip. The rocks were super slippery
Let’s go!! We’re here all weekend! @indypopcon thank you bringing us to meet the fans! Great people here and happy 10th year anniversary!
Sometimes I still can’t believe I have an action figure….I’m so honored and blessed! I appreciate all of you fans! Great kick off already on Friday!! #fanappreciation #blueranger #foreverblue

Storm breaker in the House!!! Plus More amazing fans today! <—-swipe left. Especially lisa video 7-8 I think.  She rocked a cheer in honor of my Bring it on role! Appreciate meeting everyone today! It’s still going and we have tomorrow still as our last day here @indypopcon
Yo! @dantebasco you see us bro!!!? Last day at Indy pop con!! This amazing artist made this and you can check his other pieces at multiple comic cons! @brazenmonkey_by_john_marks

Happy Power Ranger day! I designed this new photo in honor of 30 years! I am so humbled by my fans and blessed to have so much love still after all these years! You all keep this brand alive! I have had a lot of you come to me and say how I’ve helped you through tough times and in some times Power Rangers kept you alive, and being that I went through my step father committing suicide when I was only 12 and other friends as well… I’m so happy to be apart of a show that only brings happiness to the hearts of all of you!  A show that gives you an escape from the craziness in this world and shows all of you that you too are hero’s! Red, blue, yellow, pink, green, brown, black, or white… no matter what color you are in this world. If you are righteous and just then you too are a hero in my eyes! Thank you to the producers of power rangers who gave me this platform and now my son in learning about it. The circle of life is amazing! We miss you @jdfffn you will always be a legend! And shout out to all the originals that opened the doors for us! #powerrangers @walterejones @austin_st_john @karanashley @atothedoublej @catherine_sutherland @stevecardenaspr #thuytrang & @jdfffn 

Cheers 🍻 to 30 more years! 

Big shout out and credit to left side art by @carlosdattoliart for the mighty morphin issue 107

30 years of power rangers MVP goes to my brother @jasonfaunt ….

You took me in under your wing when I was just a young buck! You taught me so much in life! You have always been a selfless friend!  I have always enjoyed giving as much as I can to you because you deserve it!  You have always been there. 

It’s so cool 30 years later our toys were re-released.  I love these photos because it represents the 24 years we have stood beside one another.  I know no matter what negative comes our way I have a positive brother in you!  Our friendship is the living representation of the dynamic team power rangers stand for. 

Cheers to many more years to come as our children grow up together!  I pray for nothing but happiness and success in your life! 

#timeforceforever #foreverredandblue

Wow…. My little man is 2 years old. The terrific 2’s!! It’s hard to realize how fast it goes by.  I’m so glad I’ve been blessed to be home with him and my wife almost every day these past two years and if I have to travel I take them with me every chance I get! My son has had a passport since 10 months 🤣 GOD is good!! I love nothing more than to make my son laugh and smile.  He loves to dance when I beat box and he can already sing on key.  He climbs up every ladder or table he finds! He is a foodie like me and his mom! He loves to travel! He’s so funny in the car too! We have so many more things to explore my son!! I love you! ❤️

God bless you all today all weekend! I pray for safe travels and great spirits! To all my fans I’ll be at @dragoncon all Labor Day weekend!! Come see me! Booth #2527 on the 2nd floor of the AmericasMart!
Great time working with @seanastin in a new movie!

Amazing day! We with my two ❤️❤️’s …Also thanks to all the fans the showed up!! Sorry I could only post 9 vids on here! I appreciate you all so much! @dragoncon

Ok next big event will be in NYC oct 12th-15th!! @newyorkcomiccon aisle 3200!!! Who’s is coming? Who can I expect to meet? Please help me come up with great questions for me to ask you when I record you for my page! Feel free to post some below! Pass this flyer along to people up in the big apple! See you soon! 🙏🏽😁

We had an amazing time celebrating Malachi’s second birthday with his family!! I still can’t believe he is two and growing so fast! He loves cars and racing like lucas!! Thank you to everyone who helped set up and watch Malachi while we finished setting up his surprise! #twofast
I love you my son! Happy birthday!
OK New York comic con has started! Come see us this weekend! Booth what’s the booth again baby #3272  me and @walterejones are here! @newyorkcomiccon
Great First day at @newyorkcomiccon

I just wanna dance! @walterejones and I are here! Let’s kick off a sold out Saturday at @newyorkcomiccon also go see the other rangers!! @jasonfaunt and @tlcyellowranger are on the 2300 hall and @catherine_sutherland @nakiaburrise @stevecardenaspr are at @rangerstop_convention booth!!
@dwaynecameronofficial and @austin_st_john are floating around too!!
Also shout out to my filipino bro @dantebasco who is here too! 
Let’s GO!!!!!!!!!!!!

My wife and I are have the best time in New York! Especially here at @newyorkcomiccon we have had some time to reflect and appreciate things in our lives. It’s always great to take time to do that! God bless you all today! 🙏🏽😁

I celebrate another birthday! Their presence is the best present.  Thank you for all the birthday texts, posts, and thank you ahead of time for all the birthday love in the comments!  I’m glad to be alive another year to rock it out with everyone! Especially these two gems! #happybirthday

Seeing the smile on their faces makes everything I fight for worth it. 

Merry Christmas!
